      <h1 style="font-size:2.2rem;font-weight:800;margin-bottom:0.5rem;">SSGC Bill Online — Sui Southern Gas Karachi</h1>
      <p style="opacity:0.9;font-size:1.1rem;margin-bottom:2rem;">Check your Sui Southern Gas Company (SSGC) bill for Karachi, Sindh, and Balochistan. Enter your 10-digit consumer number.</p>
<p>PakistanBill.online is <strong>Pakistan's only platform</strong> covering both Pakistan gas utilities — <a href="/ssgc-bill/">SSGC</a> (Sindh & Balochistan) and <a href="/sngpl-bill/">SNGPL</a> (Punjab, KPK, AJK) — plus all 13 electricity DISCOs, <a href="/ptcl-bill/">PTCL</a>, and <a href="/water/">WASA water bills</a>. In Karachi, also check your <a href="/k-electric-bill/">K-Electric bill</a>. In Hyderabad, check your <a href="/hesco-bill/">HESCO electricity bill</a>. Use our <a href="/electricity-bill-calculator/">electricity bill calculator</a> or open the <a href="/dashboard/">bill dashboard</a>.</p>
      <div style="background:white;border-radius:16px;padding:2rem;max-width:560px;color:#1a1a1a;">
        <h2 style="font-size:1.1rem;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:1rem;color:#1a3a5c;">🔍 Check SSGC Gas Bill</h2>
        <p style="font-size:0.85rem;color:#555;margin-bottom:1rem;">SSGC uses its own portal. Enter your 10-digit consumer number to view your bill directly.</p>
        <div style="display:flex;gap:0.5rem;margin-bottom:0.8rem;">
          <input id="ssgc-input" type="text" maxlength="10" placeholder="Enter 10-digit Consumer Number"
            style="flex:1;padding:0.75rem 1rem;border:2px solid #e2e8f0;border-radius:8px;font-size:1rem;"
            oninput="this.value=this.value.replace(/\D/g,'')" />
          <button onclick="checkSSGC()" style="background:#1a3a5c;color:white;padding:0.75rem 1.5rem;border:none;border-radius:8px;font-weight:700;cursor:pointer;font-size:1rem;">Check Bill</button>
        </div>
