          {[
            ["Consumer Number (10 digits)", "Your permanent 10-digit SSGC ID. Different from SNGPL's 11 digits. Used for all bill checking, payment apps, and customer service."],
            ["Meter Readings (HCFT)", "Gas consumption is measured in HCFT (Hundred Cubic Feet). Current minus Previous reading equals your monthly consumption."],
            ["Billing Quantity (MMBTU)", "SSGC converts HCFT to MMBTU for billing. 1 MMBTU ≈ 10.03 HCFT. All tariff charges are per MMBTU."],
            ["Protected / Unprotected Status", "Protected (≤0.5 HCFT/day average) consumers pay the subsidized rate. Unprotected consumers pay up to 4-5x more. This is the most critical field on your bill."],
            ["Gas Charges", "Consumption (MMBTU) × tariff rate for your category."],
            ["GIDC (Gas Infrastructure Development Cess)", "A government levy per MMBTU to fund gas infrastructure expansion."],
            ["GST (17%)", "General Sales Tax on gas charges."],
            ["Due Date", "Pay before this date to avoid 10% late payment surcharge. SSGC grace period is 7 days after due date."],
          ].map(row => (
            <div style="background:#f8f9fa;border-radius:8px;padding:0.9rem 1.2rem;border-left:3px solid #2563eb;">
